Package com.paydiant.android.core.domain.splittender

This package contains domain objects that can be used to perform operations on split tender transactions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Payment
    Request containing split tender payment information.
    PaymentResult
    Contains the processed split tender payment information.
    PaymentTenderInformation
    Payment tender information containing split tender details.
    PaymentTransaction
    The Payment Transaction containing the details of a split tender payment transaction.
    Receipt
    A Receipt containing split tender transaction information.
    ReceiptList
    List of Receipts available for the split tender transactions.
    TransactionAmount
    Class containing the split tender payment amount information.
    TransactionInformation
    Transaction information supporting split tenders
    TransactionPaymentResult
    Holds the information about a split tender payment transaction.
